message:
Your code is reading the file from a thread pool thread, and then reading the file again from the UI thread.

If you want to just read the file from the thread pool thread, use `await Task.Run`, as such:

var dt = await Task.Run(() => _sourceService.ReadFileContent(filePath));  
dataGrid.ItemsSource = dt.DefaultView;  
DataTable = dt;

if (dt.Rows.Count > 0)  
BtnCreateXmlFile.IsEnabled = true;

(Tip: you should almost always use await instead of ContinueWith)
